---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
---

<Layout title="Chaya Adamson - Remember Who You Are">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section
    class="hero-section"
    style="min-height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; position: relative; background-image: url('/images/mountains.gif'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;"
  >
    <div
      style="position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(43, 27, 12, 0.6), transparent, rgba(43, 27, 12, 0.4)); opacity: 0.3;"
    >
    </div>
    <div class="hero-floating-element hero-floating-element--top-right"></div>
    <div class="hero-floating-element hero-floating-element--bottom-left"></div>

    <div class="hero-content">
      <div style="max-width: 80rem; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
        <h1 class="hero-title">You already know.</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">Let me remind you who you are.</p>
		<p class="hero-subtitle two">For spiritually-connected, self-led humans ready to embody the next level.</p>
        <div style="padding-top: 2rem;">
          <Button variant="outline" size="large" href="/offerings">
            Explore Offerings
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission Section -->
  <section
    class="content-section content-section--light mission-section-enhanced"
  >
    <div class="section-floating-element section-floating-element--top-left">
    </div>
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center;">
      <div style="max-width: 64rem; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div class="mission-content">
          <h2 class="section-title">Mission</h2>
          <div class="section-divider"></div>
          <p class="text-large">
            Coach, guide, and mirror for the ones who <strong
              >already know</strong
            >. I help spiritually connected women come home to their truth and
            move into
            <strong>full alignment</strong>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- My Story Section -->
  <section class="content-section content-section--dark">
    <div class="section-content box-content">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">My Story</h2>
        <div class="section-divider section-divider--light"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="text-content">
          <p class="text-large">
            From the very beginning, my life was shaped by grief when I lost my
            father very early in life. My childhood trauma didn't discriminate
            and neither did the pain.
          </p>
          <p class="text-large">
            I spent years chasing a definition of all the wrong things. Looking
            for safety in places I would never find it, so not different from
            the majority of us. I was looking for love in all the wrong places.
          </p>
          <p class="text-large">
            I never stopped searching. Even in the darkest moments, I believed
            that there was a reason to feel different, more aligned, more
            peaceful, more connected to my truth.
          </p>
          <p class="text-large">
            My healing practice began when I stopped trying to be who I thought
            I should be and started remembering who I actually was. I started
            through my inner work, spiritual connection, and I found myself.
          </p>
          <p class="text-large">
            Today, I believe everyone deserves to feel at home in themselves. I
            know that when we do the work to remember who we are, we can live
            from the same. Because I believe no one should have to suffer alone.
          </p>
          <p class="text-large">
            We are not here to live in regret, to carry the sky on our backs or
            to live in the shadows of our past. We are here to embody our truth
            and live from our light.
          </p>
          <p
            class="text-large special-text"
            style="font-style: italic; font-size: 1.5rem;"
          >
            And my deepest desire is to help you find yours.
          </p>
          <p class="text-large centered" style="margin-top: 5rem;">
            I don’t believe in fixing.
          </p>
          <p class="text-large centered">I believe in remembering.</p>
          <p class="text-large centered">
            You’re not starting from scratch. You’re starting from source.
          </p>
          <p
            class="text-large special-text centered"
            style="font-style: italic; font-size: 1.5rem;"
          >
            Your knowing is sacred. Your movement is divine.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center;">
          <div class="image-container image-container--floating">
            <div class="floating-effect"></div>
            <div class="image-wrapper" style="width: 24rem; height: 31.25rem;">
              <img src="/images/img.jpg" alt="Chaya Adamson" />
              <div class="image-overlay"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What You Are NOT Section -->
  <section class="content-section content-section--light">
    <div
      class="section-floating-element section-floating-element--bottom-right"
    >
    </div>
    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">What You ARE NOT</h2>
        <div class="section-divider"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid--two-cols">
        <Card>
          <div class="card-divider"></div>
          <p
            style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.4; margin-bottom: 1rem;"
          >
            You're not here to be fixed.
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.4;">
            You're here to be witnessed, mirrored, and moved.
          </p>
        </Card>

        <Card>
          <div class="card-divider"></div>
          <p
            style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.4; margin-bottom: 1rem;"
          >
            You’re not looking for motivation.
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 300; line-height: 1.4;">
            You’re looking for resonance.
          </p>
        </Card>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy Section -->
  <section class="content-section content-section--dark philosophy-section">
    <div class="philosophy-container">
      <!-- Central animated line -->
      <div class="philosophy-line"></div>

      <!-- Philosophy items -->
      <div class="philosophy-items">
        <!-- Item 1 - Left side -->
        <div class="philosophy-item">
          <div class="philosophy-content">
            <p>
              My work is for those who have already done the seeking, who are
              already doing the work, and are ready to move with <span
                class="text-highlight">clarity</span
              >,
              <span class="text-highlight">power</span>, and
              <span class="text-highlight">presence</span> into embodiment.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Item 2 - Right side -->
        <div class="philosophy-item">
          <div class="philosophy-content">
            <p>
              There is nothing to prove and nothing to be, other than exactly as
              you already are.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Item 3 - Left side -->
        <div class="philosophy-item">
          <div class="philosophy-content">
            <p>
              Welcome to the space where your <span
                class="text-highlight text-highlight--italic"
                >knowing becomes your guide</span
              >.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action Section -->
  <section class="content-section content-section--light">
    <div class="section-floating-element section-floating-element--center">
    </div>
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center;">
      <div style="max-width: 80rem; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 4rem;">
          <p
            style="font-size: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.4; font-weight: 300; margin-bottom: 2rem;"
          >
            Through methods of <span style="font-weight: 400;">meditation</span
            >,
            <span style="font-weight: 400;">IST coaching</span> and
            <span style="font-weight: 400;">embodiment practices</span>, we go
            inward. Toward your truth, your inner knowing that already has
            everything you need.
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.4; font-weight: 300;">
            If you are done outsourcing your power and ready to move with your
            knowing, we should connect.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
          <h3
            style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 200; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 3rem;"
          >
            Ready to move in alignment?
          </h3>
          <Button variant="primary" size="large" href="/contact">
            Free Exploration
          </Button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
